<HEADLINE>
<P>
MEDIA TREATMENT OF THE 'HILARY IN HIDING' CASE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
I want to thank Rosenberg for restoring some of my faith in objective reporting 
through his comments about the Morgan-Foretich child custody case. 
</P>
<P>
He points out how the media can influence, either knowingly or unknowingly, 
such matters. 
</P>
<P>
The media seem to have taken up Morgan's side. Thanks to Rosenberg for his 
voice. Only time will tell in this complicated case. 
</P>
<P>
DAVID SUTTON, Los Angeles 
