<HEADLINE>
<P>
MANY LAKER FANS SAY THERE'S NOTHING FINE ABOUT NBA'S DECISION 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Mike Downey, do you know pro basketball is a team game? Yes, if I paid 500 
bucks to see Mike Tyson's rematch with Buster Douglas and one did not fight, 
I'd want my money back. Same as if I bought Prince or Madonna or Sinatra 
tickets, or Michael Crawford in "Phantom of the Opera." 
</P>
<P>
But the people in Portland got what they paid for -- same as I got in reading 
your article. 
</P>
<P>
RIC MANDELL, Torrance 
</P>
